{"ID":"20230724002555-b44ey8v","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"icon":"1f4f3","id":"20230724002555-b44ey8v","tags":"HTTP","title":"Session 和 Cookie 的区别","updated":"20230724002606"},"Children":[{"ID":"20230724002558-a9bknbz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230724002558-a9bknbz","updated":"20230724002558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"我们先来看 Session 和 Cookie 的概念吧："}]},{"ID":"20230724002558-ptumd8f","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20230724002558-ptumd8f","updated":"20230724002558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20230724002558-hhgsbqz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20230724002558-hhgsbqz","updated":"20230724002558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20230724002558-dx4qj2x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230724002558-dx4qj2x","updated":"20230724002558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Cookie 是保存在客户端的一小块文本串的数据。客户端向服务器发起请求时，服务端会向客户端发送一个 Cookie，客户端就把 Cookie 保存起来。在客户端下次向同一服务器再发起请求时，Cookie 被携带发送到服务器。服务器就是根据这个 Cookie 来确认身份的。"}]}]},{"ID":"20230724002558-sp4gkv3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20230724002558-sp4gkv3","updated":"20230724002558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20230724002558-958emc4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230724002558-958emc4","updated":"20230724002558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"session 指的就是服务器和客户端一次会话的过程。Session 利用 Cookie 进行信息处理的，当用户首先进行了请求后，服务端就在用户浏览器上创建了一个 Cookie，当这个 Session 结束时，其实就是意味着这个 Cookie 就过期了。Session 对象存储着特定用户会话所需的属性及配置信息。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20230724002558-gz8emgn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230724002558-gz8emgn","updated":"20230724002558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Session 和 Cookie 的区别主要有这些："}]},{"ID":"20230724002558-kghu6gh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230724002558-kghu6gh","updated":"20230724002558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"img"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"file://E:/Typora%20picture/1648344513597-40e479f8-f8f1-4d19-953e-58a67959ae45.png?lastModify=1690129542"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20230724002558-mvk709k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230724002558-mvk709k","updated":"20230724002558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"来看个图吧："}]},{"ID":"20230724002558-phkg9bq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230724002558-phkg9bq","updated":"20230724002558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"img"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"file://E:/Typora%20picture/1648344513602-d581e6dd-773d-4485-aabc-ff4e75badc34.png?lastModify=1690129542"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20230724002558-yin5wej","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20230724002558-yin5wej","updated":"20230724002558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20230724002558-np81ak6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20230724002558-np81ak6","updated":"20230724002558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20230724002558-t9anqp7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230724002558-t9anqp7","updated":"20230724002558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"用户第一次请求服务器时，服务器根据用户提交的信息，创建对应的 Session，请求返回时将此 Session 的唯一标识信息 SessionID 返回给浏览器，浏览器接收到服务器返回的 SessionID 信息后，会将此信息存入 Cookie 中，同时 Cookie 记录此 SessionID 是属于哪个域名。"}]}]},{"ID":"20230724002558-ege8o3z","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20230724002558-ege8o3z","updated":"20230724002558"},"Children":[{"ID":"20230724002558-0d1ewby","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230724002558-0d1ewby","updated":"20230724002558"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"当用户第二次访问服务器时，请求会自动判断此域名下是否存在 Cookie 信息，如果存在，则自动将 Cookie 信息也发送给服务端，服务端会从 Cookie 中获取 SessionID，再根据 SessionID 查找对应的 Session 信息，如果没有找到，说明用户没有登录或者登录失效，如果找到 Session 证明用户已经登录可执行后面操作。"}]}]}]}]}